title: 114: Ranking the rookie quarterbacks
itunes:title: 114: Ranking the rookie quarterbacks
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down Marcus Mariota and Jameis Winston heading into their second season. The guys also rank the rookie quarterbacks based off of their preseason performances. DJ, Bucky, and Producer Sully wrap the show by giving their week 1 College Football picks.
